replies.body:
Junglers are poor:

{{item:1324}} {{item:3723}} {{item:3142}} {{item:3085}} {{item:3035}} {{item:3102}} 

But AD Carry items are good if you're ahead and Trinity force too I guess - GA has good synergy with her ultimate but is weak now and Devourer is in a weird spot because they nerfed it specifically for her (only procs every 4th hit) and Blade of the Ruined king is not exceptional because it has an anti-synergy with her passive because of the fact it becomes weaker faster because of her already having % current HP damage (she chunks them down for their max health % from W and her passive % current health damage sort of works against blade of the ruined king which does the same thing so you are essentially making her passive and blade of the ruined king weaker by taking 2 forms of % current HP damage and sort of going against the concept of her passive.
